3. cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) is another possible category as the paper deals with inferring label spaces using optimization techniques, which is a common problem in AI. 
4. cs.GR (Graphics) is a possible category as stereo matching is also used in computer graphics for creating 3D models. 
5. cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms) is a possible category as the paper proposes a new move making scheme using graph cuts, which is a common algorithmic technique.
